<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>WhatsApp Gateway Docs</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 font-sans">
    <header class="bg-green-600 text-white py-6">
        <div class="container mx-auto text-center">
            <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold">WhatsApp Gateway API Documentation</h1>
            <p class="mt-2">Comprehensive guide to integrate and use the API.</p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="container mx-auto my-10 px-6">
        <section class="bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg p-6">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Overview</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                The WhatsApp Gateway API allows you to send text messages and media to WhatsApp numbers programmatically.
                Below are the available endpoints and their usage instructions.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mt-8 bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg p-6">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">API Endpoints</h2>

            <div class="mb-6">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">1. Send Message</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                    This endpoint allows you to send a text message to a specific phone number.
                </p>
                <table class="table-auto w-full mt-4 text-left text-gray-700 border-collapse border border-gray-200">
                    <thead>
                        <tr class="bg-gray-100">
                            <th class="px-4 py-2 border border-gray-200">HTTP Method</th>
                            <th class="px-4 py-2 border border-gray-200">Endpoint</th>
                            <th class="px-4 py-2 border border-gray-200">Description</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="px-4 py-2 border border-gray-200">POST</td>
                            <td class="px-4 py-2 border border-gray-200">/send-message</td>
                            <td class="px-4 py-2 border border-gray-200">Sends a text message.</td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
                <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
                    <strong>Request Body:</strong>
                </p>
                <pre class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 p-4 rounded text-sm">
{
  "phoneNumber": "string (required)",
  "message": "string (required)"
}
                </pre>
                <p class="mt-2 text-gray-700">
                    <strong>Response:</strong> Returns a status message indicating success or failure.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">2. Send Media</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                    This endpoint allows you to send media (images, videos, etc.) to a specific phone number, with an optional text message.
                </p>
                <table class="table-auto w-full mt-4 text-left text-gray-700 border-collapse border border-gray-200">
                    <thead>
                        <tr class="bg-gray-100">
                            <th class="px-4 py-2 border border-gray-200">HTTP Method</th>
                            <th class="px-4 py-2 border border-gray-200">Endpoint</th>
                            <th class="px-4 py-2 border border-gray-200">Description</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="px-4 py-2 border border-gray-200">POST</td>
                            <td class="px-4 py-2 border border-gray-200">/send-media</td>
                            <td class="px-4 py-2 border border-gray-200">Sends media with an optional caption.</td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
                <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
                    <strong>Request Body:</strong>
                </p>
                <pre class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 p-4 rounded text-sm">
{
  "phoneNumber": "string (required)",
  "media": "string (required - URL to media)",
  "message": "string (optional)"
}
                </pre>
                <p class="mt-2 text-gray-700">
                    <strong>Response:</strong> Returns a status message indicating success or failure.
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="bg-gray-800 text-white py-4">
        <div class="container mx-auto text-center">
            <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> WhatsApp Gateway. All Rights Reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>

